  "description": "A vibrant sunset scene over a calm body of water. A silhouette of a city skyline and rolling hills are visible in the distance under a fiery orange and red sky. A bridge spans the water, connecting the mainland to an island. In the foreground, dark green shrubs and trees frame the view. A winding path of light reflects on the water, likely from boat traffic. The overall impression is one of serenity and natural beauty.",
